# Elk OS — portal build-context excludes
# The context is ./.build (a frozen archive). Keep it lean: node_modules and
# .next are reinstalled/rebuilt in-image, and the rest is dev-only noise that
# would only bloat the context and bust layer caching.

node_modules
.next
.git
.pnpm-store
coverage
.idea
.vscode
__tests__
__fixtures__
*.test.ts
*.test.tsx
# Dev-only Playwright/Cosmos capture routes. They 404 outside development and
# some import from the excluded __fixtures__ tree, so keeping them would break
# `next build` in-image (module-not-found). Excluding the whole tree also keeps
# future AE syncs from breaking when a new preview route imports a fixture.
app/screenshot-preview
playwright-report
test-results
.playwright-screenshots
directus-sync-dump
deno.lock
package-lock.json
*.log
.DS_Store
